OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTax break for businesses   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmade permanent             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A tax break which allows businesses to 
OL,6, deduct the full cost of investing in   
OL,7, machinery and equipment from their tax 
OL,8, bill has been made permanent.          
OL,10,FIn his Autumn Statement, Chancellor    
OL,11,FJeremy Hunt called it the "largest     
OL,12,Fbusiness tax cut in modern British     
OL,13,Fhistory", but this was disputed by an  
OL,14,Feconomics think tank.                  
OL,16,FBig business groups praised the policy,
OL,17,Fwhich had been due to end in 2026.     
OL,19,FIt is hoped it will encourage firms to 
OL,20,Finvest and lead to economic growth.    
